title: BRIEF-Docdata says IAI Industrial Systems to supply 3 passport personalization systems to Asian country
text:
BRIEF-Docdata says IAI Industrial Systems to supply 3 passport personalization systems to Asian country 
Oct 15 Docdata NV : 
* Says IAI Industrial Systems BV will supply three passport personalization systems to an Asian country 
* Bookmaster one system will be delivered and installed in 2016 
Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
